1. To install a "*.deb" software

sudo dpkg -i SOFTWARE_NAME.deb

2. If you encounter dependency issues lke, "dpkg: error processing package mysql-workbench-community (--install):
 dependency problems - leaving unconfigured", fix dependency issue with below command.
 
 sudo apt-get -f install
 
3. Then try to reinstall the package with 1st command.
